7 (2) The total number of people served;
8 (3) The average benefit in dollars received by each household; and
9 (4) The number of households that became ineligible to receive benefits.
10 2. Nothing in this section shall require the disclosure of personally identifiable
11 information. The department shall not report confidential information and use only
12 aggregate data.
